Package: OPUSdata
Type: Package
Title: Transform Bruker OPUS spectra exports to usable format
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tobias Stalder
Maintainer: Tobias Stalder <tobias.stalder.geo@outlook.com>
Description: This package holds functions to transform .dpt export data from Bruker OPUS
    into data frames, long format and export as csv (E.g. spectral absorbtion data from particle measurements).
